title: Maclaren Stroller w, Travel Bag Renton
text: Maclaren Stroller w/ Travel bag (Renton) Stroller in Seattle, WA Originally Posted On: SpreadMyAd Additional Comments: Maclaren Quest Stroller. Comes with Travel bag for safe airplane check-in. Bag is big enough to stuff other baby items, so you can free up carry-on space, such as diapers, etc. Sunshade broken, but include, fixable if you're handy. Rain fly included, but only usable if you fix the sunshade. Also included is a stroller mesh storage caddy (pictured)
